Steps to Set Up the Chatbot:
Frontend (HTML, CSS, JavaScript) for chatbot UI
Backend API (Node.js with Express or Python with Flask) to handle responses based on Scruter's purpose.

Running the Backend
Install Flask if you haven’t already:
pip install flask

Run the Flask app:
python app.py

Integrate Chatbot on Website
Once you deploy your Flask server, update the URL in the JavaScript function fetchResponse() in the HTML code with your server’s public IP or domain.
